+## VAIOS-G040 Operator Shell Evidence
+
+This mockup is the Hallucinate App operator console contract for the virtual AI
+OS desktop. Hallucinate App owns the shell chrome, daemon controls, session
+status, and recovery actions; SwissKnife owns the virtual desktop canvas and ORB
+tool surfaces launched inside that shell.
+
+The operator console must expose these VAIOS-G040 surfaces together:
+the task monitor, app launcher, ORB inspector, and session replay panes are
+first-class shell regions rather than separate demos.
+
+| Surface | Operator-visible proof |
+| --- | --- |
+| Task monitor | Shows queued, running, blocked, and completed daemon tasks with source task id, active branch, validation command, and retry-budget status. |
+| App launcher | Opens SwissKnife Virtual Desktop, Daemon Manager, System Monitor, and future descriptor-driven MCP++ apps from the same shell menu. |
+| ORB inspector | Shows discovered ORB descriptors, selected operation, required capabilities, policy decision, bridge target, and last receipt CID. |
+| Session replay | Replays session events from daemon start through ORB invocation, display bridge receipt, validation result, and rollback action. |
+
+The ORB display harness evidence term maps the operator console to the
+hardware-free SwissKnife test path
+`swissknife/test/mcp-plus-plus/meta-glasses-display-harness.test.ts`. That
+harness proves descriptor publish, widget compile, ORB discover/bind/invoke,
+bridge receipt capture, and display fallback behavior before the operator shell
+surfaces those events in the ORB inspector and session replay panes.
+
+### Operator Console Layout
+
+```
+┌─ Hallucinate App operator console ────────────────────────────────────────┐
+│ Session: hao-064-attempt-1     Daemons: 3/3 running     ORB: connected     │
+├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
+│ Task monitor                     │ SwissKnife virtual desktop              │
+│ - HAO-064 running                │ ┌─ App launcher ──────────────────────┐ │
+│ - Validation: pending            │ │ Terminal  Files  ORB Tools  Replay  │ │
+│ - Retry budget: clean            │ └─────────────────────────────────────┘ │
+│                                  │                                         │
+│ ORB inspector                    │ Session replay                         │
+│ - Descriptor: task-progress      │ - daemon-started                       │
+│ - Operation: render_widget       │ - orb-discovered                       │
+│ - Policy: allowed                │ - widget-rendered                      │
+│ - Receipt: sha256:...            │ - validation-passed                    │
+└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
+```
+
